            * rendering/RenderTable.cpp:
            (WebCore::RenderTable::addChild): remove beforeChild
            setting to afterPseudoElementRenderer.
            * rendering/RenderTableRow.cpp:
            (WebCore::RenderTableRow::addChild): remove beforeChild
            setting to afterPseudoElementRenderer.
